    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 Porsche 911 Turbo, featuring the legendary 3.6L Mezger flat-six engine. This example maintains its factory-original K24 turbochargers and the robust Getrag-sourced 6-speed manual transmission. Performance is optimized via VarioCam Plus valve timing and a sophisticated AWD system utilizing a viscous clutch center differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from factory-spec Bilstein dampers and four-piston monobloc calipers clamping cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, zero over-rev events on the DME report, and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a true turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
